    ('GEOG-G 109', 'WEATHER AND CLIMATE', '6132', 'Class Status', 'TuTh Tuesday, Thursday 4:20 PM–5:10 PM', 'RB 110', 'Staff', 1, 'Lecture', 'Lecture', '3', 'STUDENT RECREATIONAL SPORTS CE', ARRAY[]::TEXT[], 'What causes tornadoes, hurricanes, and other extreme weather? What is climate change and why is it occurring? Learn about weather, climate, and how they interact.', ARRAY['IUB GenEd N&M credit - Natural Science
